## Citation Styles

**AMA (American Medical Association)**
- Numbered superscript citations
- Common in medicine

**Vancouver**
- Numbered citations in square brackets
- Biomedical standard

**APA (American Psychological Association)**
- Author-date in-text citations
- Common in social sciences

**Chicago**
- Notes-bibliography or author-date
- Humanities and sciences

**IEEE**
- Numbered square brackets
- Engineering and computer science

