### Figure Requirements
- **Minimum**: 3-4 figures per paper
- **Graphical Abstract**: Visual summary of entire paper
- **Study Design**: CONSORT/STROBE/PRISMA flowcharts
- **Results**: Data visualization (bar charts, line graphs, box plots)
- **Conceptual**: Mechanism diagrams, workflow illustrations

### Figure Types
- Bar graphs: Comparing discrete categories
- Line graphs: Trends over time
- Scatterplots: Correlations
- Box plots: Distributions and outliers
- Heatmaps: Matrices and patterns
- Flowcharts: Study design, participant flow

