## Field-Specific Terminology

### Biomedical Sciences
- Precise anatomical terminology
- ICD/DSM/SNOMED-CT nomenclature
- Generic drug names first
- "Patients" (clinical), "participants" (community)
- HGVS nomenclature for genetic variants

### Molecular Biology
- Italics for gene symbols: *TP53*
- Regular font for proteins: p53
- Full organism names at first mention
- Standard genetic notation: +/+, +/-, -/-

